	(NO_SHORTNAMES): New definition.
	(xmalloc): Return long *.

	* etags.c (C_entries): Cast result of xrealloc.
	(xmalloc, xrealloc): Declare them to return long *.

	* b2m.c (xmalloc, xrealloc): Declare them long *.

	* movemail.c (xmalloc): Declare it to return long *.

